rubuquet usage:
---------------

	$ ruby rubuquet-tess.rb <src file> <language>

	supported languages are:	eng

Dependencies:
-------------

	* ruby
	* tesseract-ocr
	* tesseract language modules:
		- tesseract-ocr-deu 	(German)
		- tesseract-ocr-deu-f 	(the German Fraktur script)
		- tesseract-ocr-eng 	(English)
		- tesseract-ocr-fra 	(French)
		- tesseract-ocr-ita 	(Italian)
		- tesseract-ocr-nld 	(Dutch)
		- tesseract-ocr-por 	(Brasilian Portuguese)
		- tesseract-ocr-spa 	(Spanish)
		- tesseract-ocr-vie 	(Vietnamese)
	* ghostscript
	* djvulibre-bin
	* poppler-utils

